OL,3,CPregnant women in ICU face 12-times
OL,4,Chigher rate of stillbirth
OL,6,FPregnant women admitted to intensive
OL,7,Fcare face significant risks to their
OL,8,Fown lives as well as a 12-times higher
OL,9,Frate of having a stillbirth, research
OL,10,Fshowed.
OL,12,FResearchers from the University of
OL,13,FEdinburgh used healthcare databases
OL,14,Ffor more than 760,000 deliveries in
OL,15,FScottish hospitals between 2005 and
OL,16,F2018, examining all pregnancies
OL,17,Fresulting in a live birth, stillbirth
OL,18,For late miscarriage.
