OL,3,CPregnant women in ICU face 12-times
OL,4,Chigher rate of stillbirth
OL,6,FThe excess risk to those treated in
OL,7,FICU persists for up to a year after
OL,8,Fdischarge from hospital, researchers
OL,9,Falso found.
OL,11,FExperts say the findings demonstrate
OL,12,Fthe need for better tailored care for
OL,13,Fcritically ill patients during and
OL,14,Fafter pregnancy, as maternal age
OL,15,Fincreases.
OL,17,FMaternal death in the UK is known to
OL,18,Foccur in 12 in every 100,000 women,
OL,19,Fwhile a further 70 to 90 women develop
OL,20,Fsevere illness.
