OL,3,CPregnant women in ICU face 12-times
OL,4,Chigher rate of stillbirth
OL,6,FDeath is more common in women from
OL,7,Fethnic minorities and those living in
OL,8,Fsocially deprived areas.
OL,10,FRisk factors for severe maternal
OL,11,Fillness are increasingly prevalent,
OL,12,Fincluding more women with long-term
OL,13,Fhealth conditions becoming pregnant
OL,14,Fand increasing maternal age.
OL,16,FThe study found that one in 16 women
OL,17,Fadmitted to intensive care had a
OL,18,Fstillbirth, compared with one in 167
OL,19,Fwho are not admitted.
