OL,4,Chigher rate of stillbirth
OL,6,FThe study also showed that babies born
OL,7,Fto women admitted to intensive care
OL,8,Fwere 13 times more likely to require a
OL,9,Fhigher level of care after delivery.
OL,11,FOf the women discharged from ICU,
OL,12,Falmost a quarter were readmitted to
OL,13,Fhospital within a year ` compared with
OL,14,Fless than one in 10 of healthy mothers.
