OL,4,Chigher rate of stillbirth
OL,6,FResearchers said that some elements of
OL,7,Fpostpartum care may be better
OL,8,Fdelivered by intensive care
OL,9,Fspecialists in conjunction with
OL,10,Fmaternity experts, and recommended a
OL,11,F"more joined up and proactive
OL,12,Fapproach" is developed.
OL,14,FThe study is published in the journal
OL,15,FIntensive Care Medicine and was funded
OL,16,Fby the Obstetric Anaesthesia
OL,17,FAssociation.
