OL,6,FProfessor Nazir Lone, professor of
OL,7,Fcritical care and epidemiology at the
OL,8,FUniversity of Edinburgh's Usher
OL,9,FInstitute and director of research for
OL,10,Fthe Intensive Care Society, said:
OL,11,F"Being admitted to intensive care can
OL,12,Fbe a traumatic experience for many
OL,13,Fpatients and their families.
OL,15,F"When this happens during or shortly
OL,16,Fafter pregnancy, the impact on a
OL,17,Fwoman, her baby and family can be
OL,18,Fdevastating.
