OL,4,Chigher rate of stillbirth
OL,6,F"Our study shows that women admitted
OL,7,Fto intensive care experience more
OL,8,Fhealth problems during the year after
OL,9,Fpregnancy.
OL,11,F"Maternity and critical care services
OL,12,Fneed to develop a more joined up and
OL,13,Fproactive approach to better identify
OL,14,Fand support women who have ongoing
OL,15,Fcare needs after becoming critically
OL,16,Fill."
